279
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:08,010
Try to think about it.

280
00:24:15,970 --> 00:24:17,540
But to me,

281
00:24:18,050 --> 00:24:20,450
he's my most trusted friend.

282
00:24:21,560 --> 00:24:27,310
